THE LAST WEEK OR SO.

02:19:44.545 --> 02:19:47.544
I AM NOT CONVINCED THAT IS HOW
IT WILL CONTINUE TO PLAY OUT.

02:19:47.545 --> 02:19:55.544
I STILL THINK THE RISK IN THE
SYSTEM IS FOR STEEPER CURVES.

02:19:55.545 --> 02:19:56.544
YOU LOOK AT WHERE WE ARE
