YOU ARE SEEING THE EFFECTS OF
TARIFFS COME THROUGH.

02:20:05.545 --> 02:20:10.544
YOU SEE A LOT OF THE BREAKING
DOWN OF INSTITUTIONAL NORMS.

02:20:10.545 --> 02:20:11.544
ALL THESE FACTORS I THINK WILL
LEAD TO MORE PRESSURE ON THE

02:20:11.545 --> 02:20:14.544
