02:20:28.545 --> 02:20:33.544
WILL IT BE 1/:1 OR 1:1.5?
I JUST DON'T KNOW. LISA:

02:20:33.545 --> 02:20:35.544
I'M WONDERING WHAT THE REACTION
FUNCTION IS TO WEDNESDAY'S

02:20:35.545 --> 02:20:41.544
