I THINK THE ANSWER IS BOTH.

02:20:52.545 --> 02:20:57.544
I DO THINK THERE IS AN
EXPECTATION THE FED WILL DO 25.

02:20:57.545 --> 02:21:03.544
I DO NOT THINK ANYONE WOULD BE
SHOCKED BY A MORE DOVISH YEAR

02:21:03.545 --> 02:21:04.544
COULD THAT IS WHERE MARKETS ARE
