02:21:16.545 --> 02:21:22.544
IF THIS ADMINISTRATION AND FED
IS TRYING TO GOOSE HOUSING,

02:21:22.545 --> 02:21:25.544
THAT IS AN AREA THAT HAS PULLED
DOWN INFLATION.

02:21:25.545 --> 02:21:26.544
IT HAS BEEN A DISINFLATIONARY
ENVIRONMENT ON THE HOUSING

02:21:26.545 --> 02:21:30.662
FRONT.
IF YOU DO PROGRAMS AND POLICIES

02:21:30.663 --> 02:21:36.544
TO REIGNITE HOUSING, THAT
SHOULD ALSO PUT PRESSURE ON THE

02:21:36.545 --> 02:21:41.544
