WHAT DO YOU LIKE RIGHT NOW?

02:21:41.545 --> 02:21:45.544
ARE YOU GOING TO HIGH-YIELD
BONDS AND CASH? GREG:

02:21:45.545 --> 02:21:47.544
WE LIKE WHAT WE CONTINUE TO
