02:22:19.545 --> 02:22:22.294
I STILL THINK THE BACK END OF
THE CURVES ARE QUITE

02:22:22.295 --> 02:22:24.544
SUSCEPTIBLE HERE. JONATHAN:
I WOULD LOVE YOUR RESPONSE TO

02:22:24.545 --> 02:22:34.544
THIS THAT JUST CAME IN.

