WHEN YOU AGREE WITH THAT, IS
THAT THE RISK INTO WEDNESDAY?

02:22:37.545 --> 02:22:38.544
GREG:
I THINK THAT IS A PERSISTENT

02:22:38.545 --> 02:22:43.544
